'''Dr. Monique Nsanzabaganwa''' ni '''umunyarwandakazi''' w'impuguke mu ubukungu; akaba ari Guverineri wungirije wa [https://bnr.rw/home/ Banki nkuru y' u Rwanda], kuva muri Gicurasi 2011.

== Ubuzima bwambere nuburere ==
'''Nsanzabaganwa''' yavutse ahagana mu mwaka wa 1971, yize amashuri abanza na ayisumbuye mu [[Rwanda]]. Afite Impamyabumenyi y' ikiciro cya kabiri cya kaminuza mu ubukungu yakuye muri [[Kaminuza nkuru y’u Rwanda|Kaminuza nkuru y'u Rwanda]]. Yize muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'epfo]] muri [[:en:Stellenbosch_University|Kaminuza ya Stellenbosch]], yahakuye impamyabumenyi y'ikirenga mu ubukungu, akurikizaho impamyabumenyi ihanitse ya [[Filozofiya]] mu ubukungu. 

== Umwuga ==
'''Nsanzabaganwa''' avuye kwiga mu mahanga, ageze mu Rwanda yabaye umwarimu muri [[kaminuza nkuru y'u Rwanda]] kuva mu mwaka 1999 kugera mu 2003. kuva mu mwaka wa 2003 kugera mu 2008 yabaye umunyabanga wa Leta ushinzwe igenamigambi muri [http://www.minecofin.gov.rw/index.php?id=2 Minisiteri y'imari ni igenamigambi]. kuva mu 2008 kugera mu 2011 yari Minisitiri w' ubucuruzi ni inganda.

'''Nsanzabaganwa''' ni umwe mabagize uruhare mu ishyirwaho ry' [http://www.statistics.gov.rw/ ikigo cy' igihugu cy'ibarurishamibare]. Kuva mu 2012 ni umuyobozi w'inama y'ubutegetsi y'[http://www.statistics.gov.rw/ ikigo cy' igihugu cy'ibarurishamibare]<ref>http://www.statistics.gov.rw/about-us/organizational-structure/board-directors</ref>.

== Umuryango ==
'''Nsanzabaganwa''' arubatse, kdi ni umubyeyi w'abana batatu: abahungu babiri n' umukobwa umwe.

